Definition: the act of constituting a political unity out of a number of separate states or colonies or provinces so that each member retains the management of its internal affairs
Synonyms: verb, change, federate, constitution, the, act, of, constituting, a, political, unity, out, number, separate, states, or, colonies, provinces, so, that, each, member, retains, management, its, internal, affairs
Category: noun.act
